Why, then, should you lift yourselves up above the congregation of Jehovah?

00:13:34.009 --> 00:13:45.009
Korah and the others made great pretenses of loyalty to God, but completely ignored the fact that Jehovah directly appointed Moses and Aaron.

00:13:46.009 --> 00:13:53.009
