00:14:30.009 --> 00:14:36.009
My father and his companions actually rebelled against Jehovah's Authority.

00:14:36.009 --> 00:14:43.009
Their envy, pride, and ambition led to rebellion, and in the end, they brought this honor upon themselves.

00:14:43.009 --> 00:14:48.009
My father saw glory, but his glory was short-lived.

00:14:48.009 --> 00:14:53.009
I'm glad, though, that my brothers and I took the right side of the issue.

00:14:53.009 --> 00:14:55.009
It must have been hard, though.

00:14:55.009 --> 00:15:09.009
Yes, it was, but that helps us to understand how important it is that we not allow friendships or family to take priority over our relationship with Jehovah and our obedience to Him.

00:15:10.009 --> 00:15:12.009
That's what fathers always told me.

00:15:12.009 --> 00:15:14.009
Yes.

00:15:14.009 --> 00:15:20.009
Ultimately, successful direction for us humans comes from Jehovah.

00:15:20.009 --> 00:15:24.009
We should trust completely in His choices of appointed ones.

00:15:24.009 --> 00:15:33.009
You see, respect for those whom Jehovah has appointed, shows respect for Jehovah's Authority.

00:15:33.009 --> 00:15:40.009
The loyalty displayed by Korah's sons moved Jehovah to act in loyalty by sparing their lives.

00:15:40.009 --> 00:15:43.009
What fine examples for us to imitate?

00:15:43.009 --> 00:15:52.009
May we never find ourselves fighting against Jehovah by murmuring or complaining against those who He has appointed to lead His people today.

00:15:52.009 --> 00:15:57.009
To see more of the good and the bad examples of loyalty among the Israelites,

00:15:58.009 --> 00:16:04.009
we encourage you to watch the entire Respect Jehovah's Authority video on JW Broadcasting.

00:16:04.009 --> 00:16:09.009
In review, how can we show our loyalty to Jehovah?

00:16:09.009 --> 00:16:13.009
First, by coming to His defense as His witnesses.

00:16:13.009 --> 00:16:18.009
Second, by maintaining our loyal support of the faithful and discreet slave.

00:16:18.009 --> 00:16:23.009
And third, by a lowly following direction from the appointed elders.

00:16:23.009 --> 00:16:30.009
As you imitate faithful examples like the sons of Korah, like David, Peter, and Paul,

00:16:30.009 --> 00:16:37.009
you will prove to be some of Jehovah views as loyal, worthy of receiving His acts of loyalty forever.
